        Version 0.1.1
        `````````````
        
        Released on April 17, 2017.
        
        - Fixed ``TypeError`` with the recent versions of pytoml_.
        
        .. _pytoml: https://github.com/avakar/pytoml
        
        
        Version 0.1.0
        `````````````
        
